{"tid":1726234,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【化武滅族】【求推爆】藍屍黑狗繼續當講笑，齊齊吸二噁英生癌生畸胎","createTime":"2019-11-16T05:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:27.000Z","uid":16678,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c93209b834f8cb55ce8cd3189f89913ebf8fb0e3","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"啲藍屍黑狗仲係度笑笑笑<br />\n你唔撚呼吸都會經皮膚吸收<br />\n而家真係陷港鏟<br />\n麻煩齊齊推爆呢啲 Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【求下大家，再唔推，香港真係玩完】核污染級別嘅dioxin (二噁英)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725783\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725783</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">極重要!!!! 中共依加用緊TG嘅二噁英幫所有香港人絶育!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723140\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723140</a></span><br />\n<br />\n另外需要大量大量文宣同民間傳單<br />\n而家淨係連登仔自己知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢幾日我要呢個香港全部人都要知！！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後極重要！！！！！<br />\n住喺燒過中國製催淚彈地方既手足麻煩著返件長袖衫褲<br />\n戴返個豬嘴、活性炭口罩（雖然未必有用）<br />\n盡量留喺室內地方<br />\n同埋真係避免長期停留喺燒過煙既區域<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好當講笑<br />\n影響唔會短期發生<br />\n藍屍黑狗就由得佢<br />\n手足仲要睇住香港光復<br />\n<br />\n天祐香港民族"},{"pid":"6b2fc5d051cc50c19b9d36867ac0e7c3b534278e","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"未攬炒經濟就已經攬炒緊香港民族！！！！！"},{"pid":"fea910d6344ff0ea2f344c36d9f56b8eb077062a","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:29:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec8b7fdf239be442aa25b9fb64e8d6798bb32400","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dcbc764e8ac39b64eea493c9bdcaca877914acb","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe1f868b513194b3f4614f105866c7578797d0ef","tid":1726234,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"呢2日做文宣 ，星期日 去集會，和你shop"},{"pid":"8950bfaefc30480b3ddceb2b6277afaea35f9d2c","tid":1726234,"uid":184500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"【擺明分化post】公食二噁英 乸玩3P<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726235</a>"},{"pid":"1d5d054d3410d9870044509dfe96aee077ffdd23","tid":1726234,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66cfcfc9c3ca3f463eddba88680117eef559f498","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26d13558b6227d941df8be910139b1ab1a22dda2","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:40:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b36b62f982827bd95c721df464d42b46212ed8d","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"498d3799183d7cf07c013f3262c6e94111cb4df1","tid":1726234,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"246e9e5f5d59bc5d3afa707552680770137cc945","tid":1726234,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"5904eb9f0a0cd22e09d72b0dbc98173f0427dc7f","tid":1726234,"uid":237295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"黎明來到 要光復這香港"},{"pid":"79f6b853a36b6418800c1c527eae81a2aa08f976","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aed14f16cb00689f7167dceb9afd44e9990e72c7","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62b60047603162f91b164e799c78dcb3c7ce0f4e","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf5afac6212f13cb01fbc44ea1172e6eddb2e72f","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec6798c5930560a60ae4d4a6bacce90f1ba3c4f1","tid":1726234,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"港豬大叔:你班細路阻人返工時又唔講解決方法,又唔識拋返個波俾政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722858\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722858</a><br />\n今日係港鐵排隊時,有個阿叔發皮氣,係咁大罵,話暴徒搞搞震,阻住佢返工,之後我同佢講:<br />\n<br />\n我:你知唔知上星期有學生墜地受重傷,最後因<span style=\"color: red;\">警方刻意阻撓救護車救人而死亡</span>,亦有女學生因途經警署而<span style=\"color: red;\">被輪姦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,所以先決定大罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大叔:有啲咁既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我:其實你知唔知<span style=\"color: red;\">催淚彈好毒</span>,會令人冇仔生或者生畸胎兼生癌,而且其毒性會隨風飄散,全香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">冇一幸免</span><br />\n大叔:我個仔上年先娶老婆,<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔想冇孫抱呀,亦唔想生癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n大叔:咁而家點算?點樣先唔會中毒?點樣先可以正常返工,過返正常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n我:好簡單,就係<span style=\"color: red;\">政府答應五大訴求,咁件事就完</span>,唔會再有人因而受傷,受阻<br />\n<br />\n大叔:<span style=\"color: red;\">頂你,咁你地有唔早講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,你班細路係到阻路塞鐵,咁你都要解釋下,講下解決方法先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,大聲講又好,嗌咪又好,貼文宣係自己個身又好,貼係路障又好,連儂牆又好,最緊要簡單易明,字要大隻,連儂牆以外資訊唔好太多,解釋上面三點就夠,要貼係當眼處,唔係咁我地點知原來解決問題主動權喺係政府手上,拋返個波俾政府咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n大叔講完後,終於上到車返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a26039f430784e6e7292e1b23bc589961ea3267","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31fa218872eab6409412c08bf8937c9ec8012138","tid":1726234,"uid":143124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"086ddd3d92de78f9e5b553706351c8d9537375ca","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec456c4008b2b621929d36daba5f025be9a6a93a","tid":1726234,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:49:27.000Z","msg":"推"}]}